#: /Users/alalji/Downloads/splunk/etc/apps/splunk-monitoring-console/default/data/ui/views/resource_usage_instance.xml:338
msgid "<p>CPU Usage - 100% is equal to 1 CPU core.</p><p>Process class can be splunkd server, search, Splunk Web, index service, scripted input, KVStore, or other. <a class=\"dmc_process_class_learn_more external\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a></p>"
msgstr "<p>CPU-Nutzung - 100 % entspricht einem CPU-Kern.</p><p>Bei der Prozessklasse kann es sich um splunkd-Server, Suchen, Splunk Web, Indexservice, skriptbasierte Eingabe, Schlüssel-Wert-Speicher oder anderes handeln. <a class=\"dmc_process_class_learn_more external\" target=\"_blank\">Erfahren Sie mehr.</a></p>"

#. html
